qa_pairs.question: Hi, I am keen to book for Asakusa branch. Can I know which branch is nearer to Senso ji? Also we will have 3 ladies. 2 are of age 15 and 13 and they are between 150 to 160 in height. I saw that you have plan for 2 but how about 3? Does it means I need to book a group of 2 with photography and then add another 1 separately and book another photography? Or can we just book 1 photography and 3 of us to be in the photo. Can I take family plan? Itâ€™s for me and my 2 daughters age 13 and 15
qa_pairs.answer: Thank you for your inquiry. We are pleased to inform you that all three of our locations are conveniently situated near Sensoji Temple. Our main store is located by the rear gate, which tends to be less crowded, while the other two are near Kaminarimon. For your photography needs, we offer a one-hour that includes the option to add an additional kimono, allowing all three participants to be photographed together. Please note that the 30-minute photography service is available for up to two people only. Additionally, for the two young ladies, as their height exceeds the limit for the child package, they will need to opt for the adult plan. Should you have any further questions or wish to make a booking, please do not hesitate to contact us.
